name: Fire Truck
svg_content:
<svg width="512" height="512" viewBox="0 0 512 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <defs>
    <linearGradient id="fireTruckGrad" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
      <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:rgb(255,100,100);stop-opacity:1" />
      <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:rgb(200,50,50);stop-opacity:1" />
    </linearGradient>
    <radialGradient id="tireGrad" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="50%" fx="50%" fy="50%">
      <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:rgb(50,50,50);stop-opacity:1" />
      <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:rgb(10,10,10);stop-opacity:1" />
    </radialGradient>
  </defs>
  <rect x="100" y="300" width="312" height="100" fill="url(#fireTruckGrad)" rx="10" ry="10" stroke="#9C2C2C" stroke-width="5" />
  <rect x="300" y="250" width="112" height="50" fill="url(#fireTruckGrad)" stroke="#9C2C2C" stroke-width="5" />
  <circle cx="150" cy="400" r="30" fill="url(#tireGrad)" />
  <circle cx="360" cy="400" r="30" fill="url(#tireGrad)" />
  <rect x="250" y="230" width="12" height="20" fill="#FFD700" />
</svg>
